                "name": "My Life",
                "url": "/topics/my_life"
            },
            {
                "name": "Always",
                "url": "/topics/always"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703017",
        "quote": "My own contentious relationship with gaming continued through high school and college: I still enjoyed playing games from time to time, but I always found myself pushed away by the sexism that permeated gaming culture. There were constant reminders that I didn't really belong.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Anita Sarkeesian",
            "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703017"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "College",
