    {
        "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703011",
        "quote": "Online harassment, especially gendered online harassment, is an epidemic. Women are being driven out; they're being driven offline. This isn't just in gaming. This is happening across the board online, especially with women who participate in or work in male-dominated industries.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Anita Sarkeesian",
            "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703011"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Work",
