            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703016",
        "quote": "Game creators aren't necessarily all sitting around twirling their nefarious-looking mustaches while consciously trying to figure out how to best misrepresent women as part of some grand conspiracy. Most probably just haven't given much thought to the underlying messages their games are sending.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Anita Sarkeesian",
            "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703016"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Game",
