    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703009",
        "quote": "There are people I've blocked for a long time who will still respond to every single person that replies positively to me on Twitter. I have quite a few cyber-stalkers like that.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Anita Sarkeesian",
            "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703009"
