                "url": "/topics/unacceptable"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/anita_sarkeesian_703023",
        "quote": "Developers need to start moving away from the entitled macho-male power fantasy in their games. They need to recognize that there are wider stories that they can tell.",
